14 WHEREAS, pursuant to Section 308 of Title 75 of the Oklahoma
15 Statutes, the Oklahoma State Legislature shall adopt a joint
16 resolution to approve or disapprove administrative rules.
17 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES
18 AND THE SENATE OF THE 2ND SESSION OF THE 60TH OKLAHOMA LEGISLATURE:
19 SECTION 1. The Legislature hereby approves all of the proposed
20 changes to Chapter 20 of Title 748 of the Oklahoma Administrative
21 Code filed by the Oklahoma Uniform Building Code Commission on or
22 before February 1, 2026.
